NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::UseAllModules - Release tests making sure all
    MANIFEST'ed modules pass use_oK()

VERSION
    version 0.001

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files:

    *   t/00-load.t

        A basic Test::UseAllModules test

    If a more sophisticated use of Test::UseAllModules is required, this
    plugin may not be for you. Please refer to the Test::UseAllModules
    documentation for examples and more information.

SUPPORT
  Perldoc
    You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

      perldoc Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::UseAllModules

